The '''2006 SEC Softball Tournament''' was held at the [[Georgia Softball Stadium]] on the campus of the [[University of Georgia]] in [[Athens, Georgia]] from May 11 through May 13, 2006. [[Tennessee Volunteers|Tennessee]] won the tournament and earned the [[Southeastern Conference]]'s automatic bid to the [[NCAA Division I Softball Championship|NCAA Tournament]].
