The '''Cameroon Civil Aviation Authority''' ('''CCAA''', French: '''Autorité aéronautique du Cameroun'''<ref>"[http://ccaa.aero/la-surete-de-laviation-civile-au-scanner-171/dossiers/actualite/125,structure-de-surete-d-aeroport-le-bras-seculier.html Structure de sûreté d'aéroport: le bras séculier] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813065015/http://ccaa.aero/la-surete-de-laviation-civile-au-scanner-171/dossiers/actualite/125,structure-de-surete-d-aeroport-le-bras-seculier.html |date=2011-08-13 }}." Cameroon Civil Aviation Authority. Retrieved on 11 May 2011. "La structure de sûreté d'Aéroport (SSA) est un service décentralisé de l'Autorité Aéronautique du Cameroun."</ref>) is the civil aviation authority of [[Cameroon]], with its head office in [[Yaoundé]].<ref>"[http://www.ccaa.aero/contactez-nous.html Contactez-nous] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503123415/http://www.ccaa.aero/contactez-nous.html |date=2011-05-03 }}." Cameroon Civil Aviation Authority. Retrieved on 11 May 2011. "Cameroon Civil Aviation Authority (CCAA) Siège Social: B.P : 6998 Yaoundé-Cameroun"</ref> It is also responsible for aviation accident investigation.

